rows.label: qst102108_msg0001
rows.name:
Mmmhomo! The mushrooms and
weapons are all mine, mo!

rows.label: qst102108_msg0002
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Momomo!?

rows.label: qst102108_msg0003
rows.name:
It's you, mo...! Don't
startle me like that, mo!

rows.label: qst102108_msg0004
rows.name:
Don't interrupt Bamibami's
meal, mo! Go away, mo! Shoo!

rows.label: qst102108_msg0005
rows.name:
M-more details...? Nopon like
mushrooms, that's all, mo.

rows.label: qst102108_msg0006
rows.name:
Um... If I didn't defeat the Spike
Urchons from the request, they
would come to the village...

rows.label: qst102108_msg0017
rows.name:
During the confusion, I'd raid the
armory, eat the yummy-yummy mushrooms
here, and then escape, mo...

rows.label: qst102108_msg0007
rows.name:
AHHH!! GRRRR!! I'm not
giving you the weapons, mo!

rows.label: qst102108_msg0008
rows.name:
If I don't deliver them to
the Audumbla Mercenaries, I
won't get my reward, mo!

rows.label: qst102108_msg0009
rows.name:
I see... So the Audumbla
Mercenaries are behind this.

rows.label: qst102108_msg0010
rows.name:
A group of fallen nobles who hate
the way Vandham did things...

rows.label: qst102108_msg0011
rows.name: A dirty trick.

rows.label: qst102108_msg0012
rows.name: You talk too much, mo! Go away, mo!

rows.label: qst102108_msg0013
rows.name:
If you don't go... I'll burn the
weapons and the mushrooms, mo!

rows.label: qst102108_msg0014
rows.name: (What should I do?)

rows.label: qst102108_msg0015
rows.name: Try to persuade him.

rows.label: qst102108_msg0016
rows.name: Solve this with money.

rows.label: qst102108_msg0101
rows.name:
You'll die too if you
start a fire here.

rows.label: qst102108_msg0102
rows.name:
Th-that's true... Setting a fire
in such a small place is...

rows.label: qst102108_msg0103
rows.name:
In that case, give me money, mo!
Mercenaries work for money, mo!

rows.label: qst102108_msg0201
rows.name:
You'll give me money,
mo? ...How much, mo?

rows.label: qst102108_msg0301
rows.name:
How much is your contract for?
To hand over those weapons and
sell that information?

rows.label: qst102108_msg0303
rows.name: I'll give you 30,000G.

rows.label: qst102108_msg0304
rows.name: Whaaa?! So much?!

rows.label: qst102108_msg0305
rows.name: I'm buying those weapons, and you.

rows.label: qst102108_msg0306
rows.name:
On top of that, you can have as
many mushrooms as you like.

rows.label: qst102108_msg0307
rows.name:
Thirty thousand... Mushrooms...
You have a deal, mo!!

rows.label: qst102108_msg0308
rows.name:
A mercenary works for their
reward... Money is something
you can trust, after all.

rows.label: qst102108_msg0309
rows.name:
One day, I hope I can have
friends I can trust with just
my heart, like Vandham did...

rows.label: qst102108_msg0310
rows.name:
Ah, you've been a great help.
Sorry for making such a demand.

rows.label: qst102108_msg0311
rows.name:
Okay, I'll return the weapons,
mo! And then, I'll eat mushrooms,
mo! Time to feast, mo~!
